prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, clinging upside down to a colorful party streamer that sags comically under its weight. The sloth has a blissfully sleepy, slightly bewildered expression. Below the streamer, a single, beautifully wrapped gift box has tipped over, with a small piece of cake and a lone, unlit candle lying beside it. In the center, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds against a clean, light background.
